title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Chittagong · 3 bedrooms · 3 beds · 3 baths
listing_description: Relax with the whole family at this peaceful place to stay. Shops, cleaner, restaurants in the neighborhood with in 5-10 minutes distance.  24/7 watch and very cooperative.

Come and stay in this spacious, stylish and serene space with your friends and family. Brand new flat with all needs and wants; fully furnished with TV, Wi-Fi, microwave, fridge, hot water kettle, and cutlery. Every room is equipped with dresser, side table and fan to stay cool. Have 24 hr security service and friendly caretaker; centrally located within 10-15 mins of CNG ride to New Market, GEC, Khulshi, Agrabad, Mimi Supermarket, etc. If car service is needed, have trusted driver.
